snippet.title: Character Tales - "Zhongli: An Additional Expense" | Genshin Impact
snippet.description:
An account of some small happenings from before the Traveler came to Liyue and viewed the Rite of Descension.
Hu Tao, director of Wangsheng Funeral Parlor, often entrusts the undertaker "Ferrylady" to assist their consultant Zhongli in his work...
